title: Presidio Tunnel Tops | San Francisco Must See | The Presidio (San Francisco)
description: Presidio Tunnel Tops is the starting point for national park adventures, with Golden Gate Bridge views, trails, nature, picnic spots, and one of the best playgrounds in San Francisco.
